longBusinessSummary: WestMountain Gold, Inc., an exploration stage mining company, explores gold properties in the United States. It owns 100% interests in the Terra project consisting of 339 mining claims, including 5 unpatented lode mining claims covering an area of 55,040 acres located in Alaska. The company is based in Fort Collins, Colorado.
